 On Feb 17, 2011, at 10:51 AM, Pierpaolo Bernardi wrote:
 
 > On Thu, Feb 17, 2011 at 16:21, Robby Findler
 > <robby@eecs.northwestern.edu> wrote:
 >> I'm not able to reproduce this behavior. Here are the precise steps I
